(54, 1, '2021-10-22 09:50:13', '2021-10-22 09:50:13', '{\n    \"widget_block[26]\": {\n        \"value\": {\n            \"raw_instance\": {\n                \"content\": \"<aside id=\\\"blog-mantra-author-bio-2\\\" class=\\\"widget blogger text-center\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"widget-title title-sidebar\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"widget-title\\\">Author Bio</h3>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\\\"autor-bio-wrapper\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"textwidget\\\">\\n<figure>\\n                                            <img width=\\\"425\\\" height=\\\"425\\\" src=\\\"https://www.lilyturfthemes.com/demo/blog-mantra/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-blog-mantra.jpg\\\" class=\\\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" srcset=\\\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aG3-PdES5dw/XvWicjsM-CI/AAAAAAAAfLw/XhMYaCkZRgc8vBZ69ZwET1IjANGnfJ1RQCK4BGAYYCw/s139/krishna%2Bniraula%2Bcopy.jpg 425w, https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aG3-PdES5dw/XvWicjsM-CI/AAAAAAAAfLw/XhMYaCkZRgc8vBZ69ZwET1IjANGnfJ1RQCK4BGAYYCw/s139/krishna%2Bniraula%2Bcopy.jpg 150w, https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aG3-PdES5dw/XvWicjsM-CI/AAAAAAAAfLw/XhMYaCkZRgc8vBZ69ZwET1IjANGnfJ1RQCK4BGAYYCw/s139/krishna%2Bniraula%2Bcopy.jpg 300w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\\\">                                        </figure>\\n<h3> Krishna Niraula </h3>\\n<p>A young and energetic mind wishing always to move ahead along with associated colleagues, friends and juniors. A simple human being who loves his family, friends and everyone.</p>\\n<p></p></div>\\n<ul class=\\\"social-icons\\\">\\n<li>\\n                                        <a href=\\\"http://facebook.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><br>\\n                                            <svg class=\\\"svg-inline--fa fa-facebook-f fa-w-9\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" data-prefix=\\\"fab\\\" data-icon=\\\"facebook-f\\\" role=\\\"img\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 264 512\\\" data-fa-i2svg=\\\"\\\"><path fill=\\\"currentColor\\\" d=\\\"M76.7 512V283H0v-91h76.7v-71.7C76