(151, 1, '2021-10-24 08:06:15', '2021-10-24 08:06:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>बैंकिङ कसूर तथा सजाय ऐन</strong><strong>,&nbsp;</strong><strong>२०६४ का मूल उद्देश्य के-के छन्&nbsp;</strong><strong>?&nbsp;</strong><strong>साथै ढुकुटीको कारोबारलाइ ऐनले कसरी व्याख्या गरेको छ&nbsp;</strong><strong>?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>उत्तर: बैंकिङ क्षेत्रमा दिनानुदिन बढिरहेका आधुनिक तथा विस्तारित कारोबारसंगै बैंकिङ क्षेत्र अर्थतन्त्रको पर्यायवाची जस्तै भएको छ । विस्तारित कारोबारसंगै बैंकिङ जोखिम र सम्भावित कसूर&nbsp;जस्तै चोरी, ह्याकिङ आदि&nbsp;पनि बढ्न सक्ने भएकाले बैंकिङ कसूर तथा सजाय ऐनको आवश्यकता परेको हो ।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>बैंकिङ कसूर तथा सजाय ऐन,&nbsp;२०६४ का मूल उद्देश्य ऐनको प्रस्तावनामा दिइएको छ जसलाई निम्न तरिकाले हेर्न सकिन्छ:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;बैङ्किङ्ग तथा वित्तीय प्रणालीको कारोबारमा हुन सक्ने कसूरजन्य कार्यबाट बैङ्किङ्ग तथा वित्तीय प्रणालीमा पर्ने असर र जोखिमलाई न्यूनिकरण गर्न,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;बैङ्किङ्ग तथा वित्तीय प्रणालीप्रति विश्वसनीयता अभिवृद्धि गर्न र</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;बैङ्किङ्ग कसूर तथा सजायका सम्बन्धमा कानूनी व्यवस्था गर्न ।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ऐन अनुसार&nbsp;“ढुकुटीको कारोबार”&nbsp;भन्नाले एक आपसमा रकम उठाई सहमतिका आधारमा आलोपालो गरी रकम लिने वा दिने गरी गरेको कारोवार सम्झनु पर्छ । ढुकुटीको कारोबारलाइ ऐनले बैंकिङ कसूर अन्तर्गत राखेको छ र ढुकुटीको कारोबार गरेमा कैद र बिगो भराई बिगो बमोजिम जरिवाना गर्ने व्यवस्था गरेको छ ।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Q.5. What are the main objectives of Banking Offence and Punishment Act?&nbsp;</strong><strong>How has the act defined \"<em>Dhukuti\"&nbsp;</em>transaction?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With the modern and expanding business in the banking sector, the banking sector has become synonymous with the economy. Due to voluminous transactions, there are possibilities of equal risks, theft, hacking etc. in banking industry. Banking Offence and Punishment Act was thus, needed to minimize the banking risks and take proper action against the offences.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The main objective of Banking Offence and Punishment Act, is given in the preamble of the Act which is given below:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;to minimize the effects and risks that may arise due to offences in banking and financial system transactions</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- to increase the credibility of the banking and financial systems</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- to make legal arrangements regarding banking offences and penalties.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As per the Act, \"<em>Dhukuti\"</em>&nbsp;transaction means the transaction of raising money by mutual agreements and to either give or take money on one to one basis. The Act has placed the business of Dhukti under the Banking Offences and has imposed penalty and imprisonment for such transaction.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Objectives of Banking Offence and Punishment Act, meaning of \"Dhukuti\" (5 marks)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-10-24 08:06:15', '2021-10-24 08:06:15', '', 20, 'http://localhost/krishnablog/?p=151', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
